summary: It’s Time to Remake the Star Wars Holiday Special  |  Tor.com
title: It’s Time to Remake the Star Wars Holiday Special  |  Tor.com
description:
I, a ride-or-die Star Wars fan from my infancy to my almost 40 years of age, have watched the Star Wars Holiday Special exactly once, and it was plenty for me.

I would be on board with almost any remake, including this modest proposal 😂

Actually, I wonder if the team behind the Heavy Star Wars prequel edits could save the SWHS.

body:
Announcment

Hey guys!

As most of you have probably noticed, I haven’t been quite as active with my writing on here lately. Summer is one of the busiest times of the year for me, and haven’t had as much time as I would’ve liked to write.

So, to get back in the groove of writing, I’ve decided to do a 30 DAY OTP PROMPT CHALLENGE starting in August. If you guys have any specific ships you want to see during that month, PLEASE offer up some suggestions in my inbox!!

Thanks so much!

blog.description: I am a descriptivist linguist for the Mando'a language. I show what it can do, not what it MUST do. This is a place for discussion about Mando'a, and Mandalorian society and culture. Feel free to use the head cannons from this blog (or reblogged from others) in your RP or writing. All words and descriptions are taken from the mandoa.org Mandalorian Dictionary. Want to support this blog? Buy me a Kofi? OR buy some Mando'a themed items? Visit our Discord? Blog icon by Rina

title: K'oyacyi!
body:
[Koy-AH-shee!]

1. *Cheers!* 2. Can also mean: *Hang in there* or 3. *Come back safely.* Literally, a command; *Stay alive!*
